title: Get
content:
### Example #1
- Sent:
```
curl https:/jsonplaceholder.typicode.com/users
```
- Received:
```
[
  {
    "id": 1,
    "name": "Leanne Graham",
    "username": "Bret",
    "email": "Sincere@april.biz"
  },
  {
    "id": 2,
    "name": "Ervin Howell",
    "username": "Antonette",
    "email": "Shanna@melissa.tv"
  }
]
```
- Obs.: sent with header:
```
curl https:/jsonplaceholder.typicode.com/users -H "Authorization: token" -H "Content-Type: application/json"
```
